<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-439] Authentication fails when connecting to server with username and password in non ascii characters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-439</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>Tried connecting to an exchange server using NTLM authentication&lt;br/&gt;
Username : &amp;#xED;&amp;#xF1;&amp;#xEB;&amp;#xE4;&amp;#xED;&amp;#xF1;&amp;#xEB;&amp;#xE4;&lt;br/&gt;
password : &amp;#xED;&amp;#xF1;&amp;#xEB;&amp;#xE4;&amp;#xED;&amp;#xF1;&amp;#xEB;&amp;#xE4;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
I am getting 401 response.&lt;br/&gt;
Auth failed&lt;br/&gt;
Body: &lt;br/&gt;
Error: Access is Denied.</description>
